# Mem0 + LM Studio — JONBEATZ.DEV

## Scope (hard rule)

- **user_id:** `jonbeatz_dev`
- **collection:** `jonbeatz_dev_memories`
- **store:** `%USERPROFILE%\.mem0\qdrant_jonbeatz_dev`
- **Never** read/write `jonbeatz_personal`, `kristina_irwin`, or any MSC memory scope.

## Before search or infer-add

1. Run `npm run mem0:preflight` (or confirm LM Studio :1234 has any LLM loaded — default
   `qwen3-4b-instruct-2507`, shared with Hermes, no swap).

`mem0:add` (default infer=False), `list`, and `delete` skip preflight — no LLM required.

## Commands

```powershell
npm run mem0:search -- "query"
npm run mem0:add -- "text"
npm run mem0:list
```

## On failure

- Report LM Studio status once; fall back to `.cursor/docs/ReCall.md`. Run the preflight
  yourself — don't just tell Jon to run it.
